Barbra Streisand The Classic Christmas Album CD Flac TBS



The Classic Christmas Album is a compilation album, released by Barbra Streisand on September 27, 2013.[1] It consists of a selection of songs from Streisand's two Christmas albums, A Christmas Album (1967) and Christmas Memories (2001).
